<node TEXT="B.6.11 What next steps typically follow a serious reconsideration of one’s position?" ID="ID_59394579" CREATED="1754237379525" MODIFIED="1754237379525" />
<node TEXT="B.6.12 How does the act of reconsidering deepen the overall philosophical process?" ID="ID_572530223" CREATED="1754237379525" MODIFIED="1754237379525" />
</node>
<node TEXT="[7/8] 7. Refined Hypothesis" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_137320291" CREATED="1754237379351" MODIFIED="1754237379351">
