<node TEXT="B.7.10 How does offering a refined hypothesis affect the tone of the dialogue or discussion?" ID="ID_1968673119" CREATED="1754237379352" MODIFIED="1754237379352" />
<node TEXT="B.7.11 What role does careful listening play in crafting a better hypothesis?" ID="ID_1079716036" CREATED="1754237379352" MODIFIED="1754237379352" />
<node TEXT="B.7.12 How does the revision process model philosophical progress rather than perfection?" ID="ID_96931382" CREATED="1754237379352" MODIFIED="1754237379352" />
</node>
<node TEXT="[8/8] 8. Aporia / Deeper Insight" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_175868516" CREATED="1754237379352" MODIFIED="1754237379352">
<node TEXT="B.8.1 What is aporia and why is it considered a meaningful ending in the Socratic Method?" ID="ID_583939947" CREATED="1754237379352" MODIFIED="1754237379352" />
