<node TEXT="B.8.3 Why might not having a final answer be more powerful than having one?" ID="ID_1948401686" CREATED="1754237379352" MODIFIED="1754237379352" />
<node TEXT="B.8.4 What if aporia was misunderstood as failure instead of progress?" ID="ID_80119075" CREATED="1754237379352" MODIFIED="1754237379352" />
<node TEXT="B.8.5 How does aporia prepare the thinker for future inquiry?" ID="ID_1168495313" CREATED="1754237379352" MODIFIED="1754237379352" />
